task.summary: added message activity that show user messages
- added chat feature from both receiver and sender point. - refactores some layouts - fixed a bug related to undesired service unbinding on login destroy method

- fixed fragment overlap bug - added fragment backstack navigation - added pull-up to add more items in personalMessageFrag - added teeto a a sender message button - changed layout drawer - updated backstack drawer item selection code
- fixed a crash that wud be caused by a nullpointer of a material dialog in the login screen

- completed text&sound notification system -- possibility to enable/disable sound and text notification when receiving a new message. Settings - Notifications - for now, just 1 sound available: teeto!
- added a new Setting for theme because we needed a new checkBox color accent and wasn't possible with the same theme cause it uses accentColor and this can't be changed.
- added a new Setting for theme because we needed a new checkBox color accent and wasn't possible with the same theme cause it uses accentColor and this can't be changed.
